text: The Alexander Dennis Enviro350H is a hybrid-electric powered single decker bus. It has a low-floor. It was built from 2010 to 2013 by Alexander Dennis.ADL aims for Europe with 19 tonne hybrid Bus & Coach Professional 17 November 2010 ==References== ==Other websites== Enviro350 Category:Low-floor buses Category:Full-size buses
